            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-06-28</p>
<p>This update improves checkout recovery and activation reliability for
Self-Managed trials.</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed Self-Managed trial activation getting stuck after
checkout.</strong> NameQuick now recovers more reliably when checkout
finishes but license confirmation takes longer than expected.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed unclear recovery when activation cannot be
confirmed.</strong> Settings now points you back to the right activation
step instead of making a paid-but-stuck purchase look like a missing
license key.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed abandoned checkout sessions staying in
progress.</strong> NameQuick now resolves canceled or unverifiable
activation attempts more cleanly, so the app does not keep waiting on a
checkout that is no longer active.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed repeat activation retries after restart.</strong>
Pending Self-Managed trial activation now resumes with better boundaries
and stops stale retry loops when the license cannot be verified.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
